# Khuzhir, Dzhidinsky District, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Khuzhir (; , Khujar) is a rural locality (a settlement) in Dzhidinsky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 31 as of 2010.
Geography
Khuzhir is located 71&nbsp;km southeast of Petropavlovka (the district's administrative centre) by road. Zarubino is the nearest rural locality.
